---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy | MoneyJuan"
	description="MoneyJuan privacy policy explaining what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights."
>
	<div class="container page-content">
		<h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="last-updated"><strong>Last Updated: February 9, 2026</strong></p>

		<div class="content-wrapper">
			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

				<h3>Information You Provide</h3>
				<p>When you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us, you may provide:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Email address</li>
					<li>Name (optional)</li>
					<li>Any information included in messages you send us</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>Information Collected Automatically</h3>
				<p>
					When you visit MoneyJuan, we automatically collect certain information through cookies and analytics tools:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Pages you visit and time spent on each page</li>
					<li>Device type and browser information</li>
					<li>Referring website</li>
					<li>General location (country/city level, not precise location)</li>
					<li>IP address</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use our site. This helps us improve content and user experience.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
				<p>We use collected information to:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Send you our newsletter (only if you subscribe)</li>
					<li>Respond to your questions or comments</li>
					<li>Improve our website content and user experience</li>
					<li>Understand which articles are most helpful to readers</li>
					<li>Detect and prevent technical issues</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>

				<h3>What Are Cookies</h3>
				<p>
					Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit websites. We use cookies to remember your preferences and understand how you use our site.
				</p>

				<h3>Types of Cookies We Use</h3>
				<p><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function properly.</p>
				<p>
					<strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Google Analytics cookies that help us understand visitor behavior. These cookies collect anonymous data about page views, time on site, and user journey.
				</p>

				<h3>Managing Cookies</h3>
				<p>
					You can disable cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect website functionality. You can also opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

				<h3>Google Analytics 4</h3>
				<p>
					We use GA4 to analyze website traffic and user behavior. Google may use this data in accordance with their own privacy policy. Learn more about <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">how Google uses data</a>.
				</p>

				<h3>Email Service Provider</h3>
				<p>
					If we collect emails for newsletters, we use a third-party email service provider. Your email address is stored securely with that provider and used only to send you content you subscribed to receive.
				</p>

				<h3>Affiliate Links</h3>
				<p>
					When you click affiliate links on our site, the partner company may collect information about your visit through their own cookies and tracking. We do not control their privacy practices.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Your Rights</h2>
				<p>You have the right to:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time (using the unsubscribe link in emails)</li>
					<li>Request access to personal information we have about you</li>
					<li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
					<li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@moneyjuan.com">contact@moneyjuan.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Data Security</h2>
				<p>
					We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no internet transmission is completely secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security of data transmitted to our site.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
				<p>
					MoneyJuan is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, contact us immediately.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>International Users</h2>
				<p>
					MoneyJuan is based in the Philippines and primarily serves Filipino users. If you access our site from outside the Philippines, your information may be transferred to and processed in the Philippines.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this Privacy Policy as our practices evolve or as required by law. Significant changes will be noted at the top with the revision date. Continued use of the site after changes indicates acceptance of the updated policy.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="policy-section">
				<h2>Contact Us</h2>
				<p>
					Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@moneyjuan.com">contact@moneyjuan.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-content {
		padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-sm);
		max-width: 860px;
	}

	.page-title {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
	}

	.last-updated {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
	}

	.content-wrapper {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-md);
	}

	.policy-section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.7vw, 1.75rem);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
	}

	.policy-section h3 {
		font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2.2vw, 1.2rem);
		margin-top: var(--space-sm);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
		color: var(--color-text-main);
	}

	.policy-section p {
		font-size: 1.02rem;
		line-height: 1.72;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
	}

	.policy-section ul {
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
	}

	.policy-section li {
		margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.policy-section a {
		color: var(--color-primary);
		text-decoration: underline;
		text-underline-offset: 2px;
	}

	.policy-section p:last-child,
	.policy-section ul:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.page-content {
			padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-sm);
		}

		.page-title {
			margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
		}

		.last-updated {
			margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
		}

		.policy-section p,
		.policy-section li {
			font-size: 0.98rem;
		}
	}
</style>
